        <rdfs:comment>Indicator as to whether all / some of the loans in the Counterparty Group are secured by all / some of the collaterals within the Counterparty Group (&quot;Full&quot;, &quot;Partial&quot;, &quot;None&quot;)</rdfs:comment>
